##link states map, library(sf)

linkMap="https://github.com/Data-Visual-Masters/Deliverable3/raw/main/US_States_Map.json"

library(sf)
USmap=read_sf(linkMap)

#See data in map

##Call ggplot2 to create base map, add data layer, customize colors

library(ggplot2)

baseMap= ggplot(data=USmap) + theme_classic() + geom_sf(fill = 'grey', color=NA)
